track_notes: Parking for about 3 or 4 cars at the Col. Straight forward, well trodden route. Steep!
This is a circular route my walking partner devised to link three SOTA summits, to give a full day out in the hills.  This isnt the quickest way to the top.
track_title: A long walk over three SOTA summits

track_notes: Total time (including ops): 1hr 20m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards.
